# 🎵 Music Store Analytics Project


## 📌 Project Overview

This project analyzes a music store dataset using Python, SQL Server, and SQL queries.

The goal was to transform raw CSV data into a database and solve business problems related to customers, sales, artists, and music genres.



## 🔄 Project Workflow


CSV Files

⬇️

Python Pandas ETL

⬇️

SQL Server Database

⬇️

SQL Analysis



## 🛠 Tools Used

- Python (Pandas)
- SQL Server
- SQL
- CSV Dataset



## 📂 Project Structure


```
Music-Store-Analytics-Project

├── 01_Dataset
├── 02_Python_ETL
