├── 03_SQL_Queries
│       └── music_analysis_queries.sql
└── README.md
```



## 🐍 Python ETL

Used Python Pandas to:

- Read CSV files
- Create DataFrames
- Connect with SQL Server
- Load data into database tables



## 🗄 SQL Analysis

Solved business questions using:

- Joins
- Aggregations
- Subqueries
- CTE
- Window Functions



## 📊 Analysis Performed

- Senior employee analysis
- Customer spending analysis
- Invoice and revenue analysis
- Popular genre analysis
- Top artist analysis
- Country-wise customer analysis



